node.text: Even in times of darkness, memories of small kindnesses bring light. The bond I have with the ocean 🌊 is great, the nature grounds me and cleanses me. I love going to the water and get in deep thought of my sorrows and happy times, “she” hears it all as she responds to me loud and clear.

node.text:
Happiness is the best accessory, I learn that just like jewelry ; it has a life-time, it’s up to me if I want to wear my happiness or if I don’t , and the woman I am, I am becoming likes to wear her accessories every day. There will be some days where I don’t feel like wearing my accessories but as long as you know that you can wear it ANY day because it’s your choice , then you have it figured out.
Being happy is a beautiful space to be in, the art of finding happiness is called life and my journey is full of people who are positive and loving.  The lord blesses me every day, from the minute I wake up until he lays me down, through Christ I can do it all, my faith is getting bigger and bigger as I mature , it’s a beautiful thing.
Cheers to many more years, many more celebrations , I love you guys 🙏🏽🙏🏽🙏🏽.

📷 @foitlephoto

node.text: Gemini ♊️ . A lot of bad things have been said about Gemini’s however nobody in this world loves like a Gemini does. We pour our all into you, as a friend, as a partner. We talk about everything because we believe we know everything, we have the initiative to want to learn and transmit information. We want the best for you and we will make a way for you to achieve. In other words, getchu a GEMINI, YOU WILL NEVER BE BORED 😬😁😅
